[SN]TITLE[SN]
Talkback at 30: BBC News NI's Paddy O'Flaherty reports from inside his shower

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
In this latest trip down Talkback's memory lane, BBC News NI's Paddy O'Flaherty reports from inside his shower, naked, trying out a new timing device.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
7 September 2016 Last updated at 11:58 BST
The device was supplied by Northern Ireland Water to encourage people to shower in five minutes or less.
